Jayde is supposed to be out on patrol, but she's not really following 
a specific pattern.  The only thing she has on her mind right now is 
proving that she can do what any other Rogue can.  Her aimless 
trajectory eventually takes her northward, as she unwittingly points 
herself at the Maximal base.

The tiny cloaked rocket skiff streaks along its appointed path, just 
itching for an excuse to shoot at something ...
